(26, 'FaqOne', 'update', 'plugins\\PageBuilder\\Addons\\Faq\\FaqOne', 'dynamic_page', 1, 7, 'dynamic_page', '{\"id\":\"26\",\"addon_name\":\"FaqOne\",\"addon_namespace\":\"cGx1Z2luc1xQYWdlQnVpbGRlclxBZGRvbnNcRmFxXEZhcU9uZQ==\",\"addon_type\":\"update\",\"addon_location\":\"dynamic_page\",\"addon_order\":\"1\",\"addon_page_id\":\"7\",\"addon_page_type\":\"dynamic_page\",\"title\":\"Frequently Asked Questions\",\"contact_info\":\"Didn\\u2019t find the right answer? here you can ask your own questions to our support\",\"contact_info_title\":\"Contact us\",\"contact_info_link\":\"https:\\/\\/listocean.bytesed.com\\/contact\",\"contact_page_contact_info_01\":{\"title_\":[\"User Registration and Authentication\",\"Listing Management\",\"Search and Filter\",\"Payment Integration\",\"Messaging System\",\"User Reviews and Ratings\",\"Responsive Design:\"],\"description_\":[\"Allow users to create accounts and login securely. This will enable them to manage their listings, save favorite listings, and receive notifications.\",\"Provide a user-friendly interface for creating, editing, and deleting listings. Each listing should include details such as title, description, price, category, location, contact information, and optional images.\",\"Implement robust search and filter options to help users find relevant listings quickly. Users should be able to filter by category, location, price range, date posted, and other relevant criteria.\",\"If you plan to monetize your website, integrate payment gateways to facilitate transactions between buyers and sellers. This could include options for one-time payments, subscriptions, or featured listings.\",\"Enable communication between buyers and sellers through an internal messaging system. This will allow users to ask questions, negotiate prices, and arrange meetings securely.\",\"Implement a system for users to leave reviews and ratings for sellers and their listings. This will help build trust and credibility within your community.\",\"Ensure your website is optimized for various devices, including desktops, laptops, tablets, and smartphones. A responsive design will provide a seamless user experience across all devices.\"]},\"section_bg\":null,\"padding_top\":\"50\",\"padding_bottom\":\"100\"}', '2024-05-07 04:12:52', '2024-06-27 12:30:00'),
